N = 250
U = make_random_orientations(N)
t0 = timer()
for u1 in U:
    for u2 in U:
        tr1 = misori_cubic(u1, u2)
        tr2 = misori_cubic(u2, u1)
        self.assertAlmostEqual(tr1, tr2)
t1 = timer()
if self.DOBENCH:
    print('C %d pairs in %f s,  %f s per pair' % (N * N * 2, t1 - t0, (t1 -
        t0) / N))
